| Maturation stage thresholds | `systems/lifecycle.json` | per-entity JSON duplication, `combat.json` |

| Motion tracker detection | `items/motion_tracker.json` | entity `follow_range`, `combat.json` |

| Block break spawn behavior | event/behavior systems (code) | block `gameplay` JSON |

| Attachment distance / face height | facehugger `attachment_parameters` | `LifecycleConfig` defaults, domain constants |

| Entity sounds | entity `visual.*_sound` | `XenomorphType` enum switches |



**Reviewer rule:** PRs adding config keys must state owner **and** at least one rejected owner in the description.



